	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">A Guide to soloing a Rogue </div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By FiveFinger</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Feb  2, 2005, 13:18</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=A%20Guide%20to%20soloing%20a%20Rogue%20&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2FWoW%2Fguides%2Farticle_38.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="http://www.thesafehouse.org/articles/WoW/guides/printer_38.php">Printer&nbsp;friendly&nbsp;page</a></div>
